(6)Department of Economics, Faculty of Arts and Social Sciences, The Open 
University, Milton Keynes, UK.
(7)Ministry of Health of Ethiopia, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia.
(8)Global Health & Infection Department, Brighton and Sussex Medical School, 
Brighton, UK.
(9)School of Public Health, College of Health Science, Addis Ababa University, 
