2023  Aug 13.

Body appreciation around the world: Measurement invariance of the Body 
Appreciation Scale-2 (BAS-2) across 65 nations, 40 languages, gender identities, 
and age.

Swami V(1), Tran US(2), Stieger S(3), Aavik T(4), Ranjbar HA(5), Adebayo SO(6), 
